Package project.view.splendor.communication

Interface Action

All Known Implementing Classes:
PurchaseAction, ReserveAction, TakeTokenAction
public interface Action
Generic Action abstract class for blackboard architecture. Implement your own actions, representing kinds of actions performed by players in a blackboard architecture. Actions are generated by a custom ActionGenerator and performed by a custom ActionInterpreter.
